# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in real values for local development.
# `.env` is gitignored and must NEVER be committed.
#
# FastF1 itself needs no API key, so this dashboard currently reads no secrets.
# This file exists as the template for any future integration that does.
#
# Example: a weather overlay backed by a third-party API.
# WEATHER_API_KEY=your-key-here
#
# When deploying, set these as platform secrets/environment variables
# (Streamlit Community Cloud secrets manager, Railway env vars) — not in the repo.
